{"title":"致民族战士","authors":["西姆巴蒂斯"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":12,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"北加里曼丹诗选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"致民族战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西姆巴蒂斯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝已经胜过昨宵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更大的希望在明朝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今这块土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狮子已经跛了腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却还在乱吼乱叫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家人都为你祈祷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真主同你在一道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们大家在你身旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓起你火热的斗志吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚定你纯洁的心灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可别把敌人的头目轻饶！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须剥夺他手中的权力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使你的民族走上光明大道！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给勇士沙德利雅·特玛斯克"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用鲜血为人们沐浴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表示你对祖国的热爱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你承受了一切痛苦和灾难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表示你对人民的热爱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去争取独立吧……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用你充满信心和意志的胸怀。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}